    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies a new PCP functional element denoted as PCP Proxy. The PCP Proxy relays PCP requests received from PCP Clients to upstream PCP Server(s). This function is mandatory when PCP Clients can not be configured with the address of the PCP Server located more than one hop.</t>
